{"type": "article", "id": 45447, "title": "欧莱雅继承人去世，以及，匡威的 NBA 主题 Chuck Taylors 好看 |  浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-09-22T03:41:08Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 24207, "name": "Chuck Taylor"}, {"id": 2145, "name": "Converse"}, {"id": 27, "name": "Nike"}, {"id": 2200, "name": "Moschino"}, {"id": 671, "name": "Gucci"}, {"id": 37319, "name": "H&M Studio"}, {"id": 1576, "name": "欧莱雅"}, {"id": 334, "name": "优衣库"}, {"id": 41741, "name": "Hourglass"}, {"id": 44251, "name": "贝古当"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 37, "image": "img/article/article_show/201709221105596uaZNcUE8bx1AOlo.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2017/09/21/world/europe/liliane-bettencourt-dead-loreal.html?_r=1\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>欧莱雅继承人贝当谷去世，享年 94 岁</strong></a> | 贝当谷是欧莱雅创始人 Eugene Schueller 唯一的孩子，她把欧莱雅从一间染发剂公司发展为拥有 30 个品牌的化妆品集团。贝当谷也是全球最富有的女性，财富净值达到 425 亿美元。</p><p><a href=\"http://us.fashionnetwork.com/news/Uniqlo-makes-big-denim-play-with-new-LA-concept-shop,871330.html#.WcRdBMa76qA\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>今年秋天，优衣库将要在 LA 开一家“denim concept shop”</strong></a> | 这家“denim concept shop”关注在高端牛仔和零售体验上。优衣库去年 11 月在 LA 开设了一个牛仔创新中心，用来开发优衣库和 J brand 的牛仔系列。不过具体细节没有透露。</p><p><a href=\"http://www.ebrun.com/20170921/247270.shtml\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>联合利华旗下美妆品牌 Hourglass 9 月 24 日将进驻天猫</strong></a> | Hourglass 创立于 2005 年，定位高端奢侈美妆，今年 6 月被联合利华收购。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>迎接即将到来的 NBA 新赛季，Converse 推出了一个<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/09/21/converse-nba-chuck-taylor-all-star/#slide-15\" rel=\"nofollow\"> NBA 主题的 Chuck Taylor All Star 系列</a>。 </p><p>该系列共有 15 款不同的设计，将于 9 月 29 日正式登陆指定门店和官网，售价在 107 至 238 美元之间。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922105626LwFr1htpqUoDVS83.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922105621O3M4zwPY81lVWGF5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922105623y3IY7DAPcStnfu8l.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922105615UvXBPuizgcIAaHZh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922105618x7GXuJfB6AhKYjcv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922105624XM3SIdAaD0F1bZlw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922105625WcQCoXBReJb0tTl9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922105625WM6iqXyrgoZedvUG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922105627a7qpxbGDH6yChd2O.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922105627J7ObZctVNwMTy5Ru.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922105638VgF24CvUxJ3Wm9ka.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922105639REMS4oFADv3Wcyil.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709221056397gqcfS5UCzkepK84.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922105640wCTzy0Oejgi9SJcr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922105720vGUHtIrkeqJCxROE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>作为 NBA 17/18 赛季官方球衣赞助商，<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/09/21/nike-nba-warm-up-jackets/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nike</a> 发布了最新的 NBA 热身连帽衫设计，来看看： </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922105532r6o3CmyfqEPIxXYZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922105544X57ZPsLcCzAYtR2v.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922105527eiqLpjc2lxKaFyMJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922105529xj3zE06p4kAGrCN8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922105530273MEnvI0aGLOsJZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922105530dpmJK9Sseg3Nbv2q.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922105531wHXLDvMYiNu2cU70.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922105531iY0Mnp5kNILOmSWh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922105531WotbgwlLcMusj3Re.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709221055322WCY5LkhFvDRZu17.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922105535if60TUoV357zYHPp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922105538Ps1VSm2gh4oOQUxY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://fashionista.com/2017/09/hm-studio-collection-fall-2017\" rel=\"nofollow\">H&amp;M Studio 精品系列</a>发布，造型师 Ludivine Poiblanc 为它拍摄了一组值得一看的 lookbook。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922105751jk8mhigoUOSrsw7K.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.425517\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922105758MCipIolqe4yNdv5L.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.425517\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709221057582o1Sgn7RiIycaFwf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.425517\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922105758iIHQcSxw7t4eVm3C.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.425517\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922105800JZp8zNbDj1yABort.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.425517\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922105801I14JqdpkVaPD9imW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.425517\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922105803Az8iMmxPk1vgZ75N.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.425517\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922105803TCbRtqzVQ10kNHxK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.425517\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922105803xYjPtmL7C86fOiDc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.425517\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922105804pq6O5bziLZWKcgRD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.425517\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922105805zvpP1O2CblyH3ALg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.425517\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922105806kelgSxNFAm4jb9HM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.425517\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017092210580613H2W6qvjRVaBkYA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.425517\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017092210580605kCRKGOhTqWI2bA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.425517\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922105807IkAjBWayqV3Pxd0Q.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.425517\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>Jeremy Scott 入主之后，<a href=\"https://popbee.com/fashion/runway-fashion/kaia-gerber-gigi-hadid-moschino/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Moschino </a>总是不缺乏大胆、有趣的创意。这次的米兰时装周上，Moschino 推出了一系列结合朋克和芭蕾风格的服装，还把模特打扮成了人形花瓶。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922105354bhfjsBK8CTmGMWvi.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709221054000Idh8mFwXtj2caE5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709221054051bac8W7GKkioDErU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922105440gbA1jSexqZOIWi09.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922105407pyH9h2MdAKe48asG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922105411807voMscqpV2YOZA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922105413FOfwWzU9kpqjg3Qr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922105417Vf21XEr74TPAbgHj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922105417Tab4CsLWwjcPRI37.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922105430cPMx1AnYRCiEwL9p.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922105430xCh43QvkOgb698uw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922105433fLRuz3M2GPFjoSY4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922105435gtbU2lQJiNWx4ywo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922105435wNbtDSuKMgfxR6cv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922105438oI2stnb0vKZh9Sl1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>米兰时装周开幕，<a href=\"https://popbee.com/fashion/runway-fashion/mfw-2018ss-gucci-disco-beat/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Gucci </a>今年延续了复古、夸张的风格。模特们顶着凌乱的发型，带着夸张的眼镜和水晶刺绣物出场，融合了中东、中国元素的华丽服装也让人眼花缭乱。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709221101376wiQr70pBnc3JgKz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017092211013885K4c6FhVotpHMsl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922110141GhYpriMvK04fwTUy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922110141koHmA7SNGC9b8uFD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922110142GgCP3DH75eMsjORN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170922110142zFPJlXZu4bUmMa6n.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figu